<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08130</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT SUBSTANTIALLY INCENTIVIZING FILIPINO INVENTORS WITH THE END IN VIEW OF FULLY DEVELOPING THEIR INVENTIONS THAT BENEFIT THE NATION</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Intends to support Filipino inventors and promote their inventions, especially those that would benefit the community/nation.
Seeks to grant meaningful incentives “including but not limited to financial support, study and research grants, technical, material and industry support”.
